OL,3,CLife sentence for 'obsessed' ex-
OL,4,Cpartner who stabbed graduate to death
OL,6,FWarning: this article contains details
OL,7,Fsome readers may find upsetting
OL,9,FAn "obsessed" adult support worker who
OL,10,Fstabbed a psychology graduate to death
OL,11,Fin Nottingham because he was bitter
OL,12,Fabout their relationship ending, has
OL,13,Fbeen jailed for life.
OL,15,FAdedapo Adegbola, who is 40, was in a
OL,16,Fbrief relationship with Stephanie
OL,17,FIrons, who was 23. They had worked
OL,18,Ftogether.
