OL,3,CLife sentence for 'obsessed' ex-
OL,4,Cpartner who stabbed graduate to death
OL,6,FBut Nottingham Crown Court heard that
OL,7,Fhis "controlling" behaviour led to
OL,8,Ftheir relationship ending, and that he
OL,9,Fwas "not prepared to accept that".
OL,11,FAdegbola, an adult support worker who
OL,12,Fhad earlier lived at Woodborough Road
OL,13,Fin Mapperley, clasped his hands to his
OL,14,Fface and sobbed in the dock today
OL,15,Fbefore he was jailed for life with a
OL,16,Fminimum term of 25 years.
OL,18,FHe stabbed his former partner to death
OL,19,Finside her own flat in Westdale Lane
OL,20,FWest in Mapperley, on the evening of
OL,21,F21st October 2025.
