OL,6,FAdegbola, who had worked with
OL,7,FStephanie, bought two knives on the
OL,8,F16th October.
OL,10,FHe used them to kill her inside her
OL,11,Fown living room after turning up at
OL,12,Fher address when they had both
OL,13,Ffinished work on the 22nd October.
OL,15,FWork colleagues went to her home and
OL,16,Fcalled police at 10.07pm, after
OL,17,Freceiving concerning messages which
OL,18,Fmade them think Adegbola had her
OL,19,Fphone, and because Stephanie was not
OL,20,Fanswering the door.
