OL,6,FWhen police arrived at the scene they
OL,7,Fsaw Stephanie in a pool of blood on
OL,8,Fthe floor through a back window.
OL,10,FProsecution counsel Peter Joyce KC
OL,11,Fsaid she had received "devastating"
OL,12,Finjuries. The fatal injury was a knife
OL,13,Fwound to her neck which had cut her
OL,14,Fjugular vein.
