OL,6,FAdegbola had since fled the scene,
OL,7,Fhaving sat on Miss Irons' sofa as she
OL,8,Flay dead or dying on the floor. He had
OL,9,Flocked her door behind him and had
OL,10,Fleft a trail of evidence on the
OL,11,Fstreets of Mapperley and nearby
OL,12,FCarlton.
OL,14,FMr Joyce said "He discarded various
OL,15,Fitems ` his shoes, his shirt, he got
OL,16,Frid of her keys, her phone and got rid
OL,17,Fof the murder weapon, having wiped off
OL,18,Fher blood and using it on himself in
OL,19,Fan alleyway".
