OL,6,FStephanie had been preparing to apply
OL,7,Ffor a doctorate in clinical psychology
OL,8,Fbefore she was killed.
OL,10,FJudge Nirmal Shant KC told Adegbola,
OL,11,Fwho wore a grey tracksuit for the
OL,12,Fhearing, that he had caused "profound
OL,13,Fdevastation" to the loved ones of Miss
OL,14,FIrons.
OL,16,FShe said: "She was in the prime of her
OL,17,Flife and your actions took her future
OL,18,Ffrom her."
