OL,6,FProsecution counsel Peter Joyce KC
OL,7,Ftold the court Adegbola had "become
OL,8,Fobsessed with this woman and would not
OL,9,Faccept the relationship with her was
OL,10,Fover".
OL,12,FHe added: "This was a deliberate,
OL,13,Fplanned killing of a woman who had
OL,14,Fspurned him, so he decided to kill."
